            "section": "",
            "ref_spans": []
        },
        {
            "text": "We are hopeful that this special issue would provide insight into the current practice of foot and ankle problems to our readers and would also act as a useful reference for the future researchers. We sincerely hope that our readership is keeping well and staying safe in these very difficult times.",
